---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout
  title="Affiliate Disclosure - Fairly Odd Streamers"
  description="Affiliate disclosure and transparency statement for Fairly Odd Streamers."
>

<div class="section-narrow">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="content-narrow">
      <h1>Affiliate Disclosure</h1>

      <p>
        <strong>Transparency is important to us.</strong> Fairly Odd Streamers participates in affiliate programs and
        may earn commissions from products and services recommended on this site.
      </p>

      <h2>How It Works</h2>
      <p>
        When you click on a sponsorship or tool link on our site and make a purchase, we may earn a commission. This
        doesn't cost you anything extra — the price you pay remains the same. We only recommend products and services we
        believe are valuable for streamers.
      </p>

      <h2>Our Commitment</h2>
      <ul>
        <li>We only recommend tools and sponsorships we genuinely believe in</li>
        <li>We clearly mark affiliate links where applicable</li>
        <li>Affiliate relationships never influence our editorial content</li>
        <li>We regularly review all recommendations for quality and relevance</li>
        <li>Your trust is more important to us than any commission</li>
      </ul>

      <h2>FTC Disclosure</h2>
      <p>
        As required by the Federal Trade Commission (FTC), we disclose that Fairly Odd Streamers is a participant in the
        Amazon Services LLC Associates Program and other affiliate advertising programs designed to provide a means for
        sites to earn advertising fees by advertising and linking to their products.
      </p>

      <h2>Questions?</h2>
      <p>
        If you have any questions about our affiliate practices or recommendations,{' '}
        <a href="/contact/">please get in touch</a>.
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>
</BaseLayout>
